Package matthewm101

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HeatmapGenerator.HeatmapGeneratedHandler
    Defines that a class can respond to TaskGenerate or TaskRegenerate.
    HeatmapGenerator.HeatmapSetupHandler
    Defines that a class can respond to TaskSetup finishing.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HeatmapGenerator
    A class that stores the parsed data from an OpenStreetMap xml file and uses the data to produce a heatmap.
    HeatmapMenu
    A JFrame menu that displays a heatmap and presents controls that can change the appearance and backing data for the heatmap.
    LoadFileMenu
    A JFrame menu that handles the loading of an XML file and an optional image.
    PointOfInterest
    A class that stores the location and tags of an OpenStreetMap node.
    PointOfInterestParser
    An XML parser that reads the nodes of an OpenStreetMap xml file.
    StreetMapDataInterpreter
    A utility class that filters out OpenStreetMap points of interest based on whether they have specific tags.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HeatmapMenu.Preset
    An enum of useful amenity sets.
